        {
            "title": "白宮：特朗普有意讓阿拉伯國家為美國打伊朗埋單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"白宮：特朗普有意讓阿拉伯國家為美國打伊朗埋單\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IRhr_k6QRu.METa47_AlcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/3c825540-2ca0-11f1-bebd-fe50fe7d00bd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">白宮：特朗普有意讓阿拉伯國家為美國打伊朗埋單</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
